                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup

                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup

                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-oidc-iam-sa-nodeLaunchConfiguration-14d2b2a
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-03711d3b9b21b3a8e","subnet-06e8296c053e2b952","subnet-0fc2dc8f8ba906919","subnet-037f366816336db85"]
                          Tags:

                            Value: example-oidc-iam-sa-eksCluster-ef4f00f-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-oidc-iam-sa-eksCluster-ef4f00f
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
